google_play_reviews.content: We use/test conv6ations, conion, onion messenger. New account in stork using tigase.im. tapping on the lock above the chat - omemo error cannot create session. Maybe not supported? Unfamiliar with all of this so far. Another thing that is frustrating, not having or allowing a dark mode/theme. kills battery, screen and eyes especially(especially at night). Seems to be a lack of options throughout, especially compared to other similar apps. Thanks, appreciate it. Keep it up. Will update review
Nice looking client but OMEMO keys never load, making this app useless unless you don't care about privacy. Unable to test this app further as a result.
